refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraymcrypt_list_algorithms stringlib_dirini_get("mcrypt.algorithms_dir")
Gets the list of all supported algorithms in the lib_dir parameter.

&reftitle.parameters;
lib_dir
Specifies the directory where all algorithms are located. If not specified, the value of the mcrypt.algorithms_dir &php.ini; directive is used.

&reftitle.examples;
mcrypt_list_algorithms Example
<?php $algorithms = mcrypt_list_algorithms(); print_r($algorithms); ?>
